def computeTF(wordDict, doc):
    tfDict = {}
    corpusCount = len(doc)
    for word, count in wordDict.items():
        tfDict[word] = count/float(corpusCount)
    return(tfDict)

def df_to_worddict(df):
    user_link_pattern = r'&amp|@\w+[\.,]?\b|https?://[\w\./]+|[^\w\s]'
    text = df['tweet'].str.replace(user_link_pattern,'',regex=True).str.cat(sep=' ').lower()
    tokenized_word = word_tokenize(text)
    tokenized_word = [w for w in tokenized_word if w not in stop_words]

    wordDict = Counter(tokenized_word)
    tokenized_word_list.append(wordDict)
    return computeTF(wordDict, text)

tokenized_word_list = []

res = [df_to_worddict(sub_df) for sub_df in df_lst]

import matplotlib.pyplot as plt

for tkwd in tokenized_word_list:

    df = pd.DataFrame(sorted(list(tkwd.items()),key=lambda x:-x[1])[:100], columns=['word', 'frequency'])
    df = df.set_index('word')
    df.plot(figsize=(18,10),kind='bar')
    plt.xticks(rotation=90)
    plt.show()
In [19]:
zipf_df = []
for tkwd, y in zip(tokenized_word_list, year):
    df = pd.DataFrame(sorted(list(tkwd.items()),key=lambda x:-x[1]), columns=['word', 'frequency'])
    df['rank'] = df['frequency'].rank(ascending=False)
    df['year'] = y
    zipf_df.append(df)


combined_df = pd.concat(zipf_df, ignore_index=True)
for year, group in combined_df.groupby('year'):
    plt.figure(figsize=(8, 6))
    plt.loglog(group['rank'], group['frequency'], marker='o', linestyle='', label=f'Year {year}')
    plt.xlabel('Rank (log scale)')
    plt.ylabel('Frequency (log scale)')
    plt.title(f'Log-Log Plot of Word Frequencies vs Rank for Year {year}')
    plt.legend()
    plt.grid(True)
    plt.show()

from sklearn.feature_extraction.text import TfidfVectorizer
tfidf_lst = []
for sub_df in df_lst:
    user_link_pattern = r'@\w+[\.,]?\b|https?://[\w\./]+|[^\w\s]'
    text = sub_df['tweet'].str.replace(user_link_pattern,'',regex=True).str.cat(sep=' ').lower()
    tfidf_lst.append(text)
vector = TfidfVectorizer(stop_words='english')
response = vector.fit_transform(tfidf_lst)
response = response.toarray()
